{"type": "article", "id": 22985, "title": "中国结抱枕", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-29T07:08:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125948ohlFcTivpHygqtjx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是冰岛设计师 Ragnheiður Ösp Sigurðardóttir 带来的抱枕，它的灵感源于中国结。根据不同的打结方式，它也有丰富的形状，使用者甚至可以自行拆掉还原成一条粗线，然后重新打结，手工感十足。这些抱枕的表面都是由不同颜色的毛线织成，中间塞入填充，非常温暖居家。目前在 easy 上出售，<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/Umemi/sold?ref=shopinfo_sales_leftnav\">这里购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125946WwlsZph8Fz03IjD1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021259463HBAgXE9lJVsK2wY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"dragged\" style=\"height: 376px; width: 375px; left: 555px; top: 974px;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125947MPk2WFwVo5Ag74lt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125947DylEgOPTSiRJNLHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}